First- and second-trimester evaluation of risk for Down syndrome.

Ball RH(1), Caughey AB, Malone FD, Nyberg DA, Comstock CH, Saade GR, Berkowitz 
RL, Gross SJ, Dugoff L, Craigo SD, Timor-Tritsch IE, Carr SR, Wolfe HM, Emig D, 
